- Conflicts with key preferences: it’s “punchy, bass‑forward” with propulsive synth‑bass and crisp percussion. I dislike muddy or dominant low end and prefer restrained percussion and preserved micro‑dynamics; a bass‑forward, synth‑driven production is more aggressive and less analogue‑acoustic in character.
